r close intellectual exchange by involving students in the ongoing research of stanford professors undergraduate courses search for political science courses on explorecourses view a list of political science cognate courses undergraduate student resources declare the political science major petition a course for the major or minor petition a directed reading apply to the research honors track secondary links stanford home school of humanities and science contact login stanford university department of political science encina hall west suite 100 stanford california 94305 6044 phone 650 723 1806 fax 650 723 1808
